Class HALPipeline

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.SCHSRobotics.HAL9001.system.robot.HALPipeline
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    AnglePIDTunerSystem.AnglePIDTunerSystemPipeline, CameraCalib.CameraCalibPipeline, ColorspaceCalib.ColorspaceCalibPipeline 

    public abstract class HALPipeline
extends Object
    An abstract class used to store HAL computer vision pipelines. Almost a complete copy of OpenCvTracker from EasyOpenCV.

    Since:
